//4.Karma Rottnest - Australia
$id="802";
$bannerImages=array("https://karmagroup.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/cuisine-karma-rottnest.jpg","https://karmagroup.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/header-karma-rottnest-aerial.jpg","https://karmagroup.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/karma-room.jpg");
$title = "Welcome to Karma Rottnest, Western Australia";
$subTitle = "<h2>Luxury Accommodation in Rottnest Island, WA</h2>";
$description = "<h2><h3>Secluded beaches, turquoise seas and the friendliest marsupials you&#8217;ll ever meet: just three good reasons to come to Rottnest Island, Australia&#8217;s best-kept secret&#8230;</h3><p>Amid these stunning natural surroundings, Karma Rottnest Lodge offers a serene retreat in which to relax, recharge and indulge yourself with sumptuous spa treatments and fine cuisine. With so much to discover across this beautiful island, each day brings a brand new adventure. The only caveat? You&#8217;ll never want to leave&#8230;</p>";

$amenities=array("<p>The premier place to stay on Rottnest Island, Karma Rottnest Lodge can host up to 246 guests – but its spacious, sprawling design allows plenty of room for everyone to savour their own little piece of paradise.</p>
<p>Relax by the pool with a signature cocktail, make new friends with a game of barefoot bowls or indulge yourself with a blissful spa treatment. The choice is all yours...</p>",array(array("Riva restaurant","<p>From wood-fired pizzas to three-course feasts: our relaxed Mediterranean-inspired eaterie offers a variety of exceptional dishes and a wonderful wine and cocktail list to match.</p>","https://karmagroup.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/Dining_at_Riva-1024x682.jpeg","",""),array("Karma Spa","<p>Asian Foot Rituals, bespoke massages or fabulous facials: choose from our boutique menu of out-of-the-ordinary therapies and treatments in oh-so-soulful surroundings. You&#8217;re here to relax, after all&#8230;</p>","https://karmagroup.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/Headline_B_spa.jpg","",""),array("Gov's sports bar","<p>With live music, DJs, comedy nights, quizzes, pool, darts and more, our sports bar is the perfect place to relax with friends old and new after a sun-kissed day of adventure.</p>","https://karmagroup.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/Govs_Sports_Bar-1.jpeg","",""),array("Golf","<p>Get ready to tee off in style. Rottnest Golf Club boasts newly grassed greens and reticulated fairways for a challenging but rewarding game. Not brought your clubs? No problem! You can hire a set from our pro shop.</p>","https://karmagroup.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/Golf-1024x613.jpeg","",""),array("Bowls","<p>It&#8217;s time to feel the sun on your face and the grass between your toes with a gentle game of barefoot bowls – one of Australia&#8217;s hippest and fastest-growing sports.</p>","https://karmagroup.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/Bowls.jpeg","",""),array("Conference facilities","<p>Karma Rottnest Lodge can comfortably host groups of up to 110 in its fully-equipped conference facilities. And with a menu of out-of-session activities that includes movie screenings, bike tours and wine-tastings, we can guarantee the ultimate morale-booster. Interested? Our experienced team are here to help tailor-make your ideal itinerary.</p>","https://karmagroup.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/Conference_Facilities-1024x682.jpeg","","")));

$accomodation=array("Rooms and apartments","<p>Whether you're travelling solo or here with the family, there's a wide choice of comfortable, well-equipped rooms and apartments – all with en-suite bathrooms, ceiling fans, TVs and many other thoughtful extras – to suit your needs. It's time to select your ideal island hideaway...</p>",array(array("Deluxe room","https://karmagroup.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/Karma-Rottnest-Deluxe-Room.jpg","<p>Perfect for couples, small families or groups of friends, these rooms are located in the historic Palm Court area and boast two beds – a queen and a single. French doors open on to a shared verandah, where you can kick back with a cocktail at the end of the day.</p>"),array("Family room","https://karmagroup.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/Karma-Rottnest-Family_Room.jpg","<p>Ideal for families, these serviced apartments boast two bedrooms – one with a queen-size bed, the other with bunks – plus a lounge area and well-equipped kitchen with dishwasher and washing machine. The outdoor verandah overlooks pretty Heritage Common.</p>"),array("Lakeside standard room","https://karmagroup.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/Karma-Rottnest-Lakeside-Standard-Room.jpg","<p>Great for families or groups of friends, these rooms contain a queen-size and two single beds, plus a lounge area and private balcony. As the name suggests, they&#8217;re close to a picturesque lake.</p>"),array("Premium lakeside room","https://karmagroup.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/Karma-Rottnest-Premium_Lakeside_Room.jpg","<p>These recently refurbished rooms provide the pinnacle of understated luxury, including a sumptuous king-size bed, a day bed and top-quality designer furnishings and fittings throughout. The private balcony overlooks the beautiful Governor&#8217;s Lake.</p>"),array("Quod room","https://karmagroup.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/Karma-Rottnest-Quod_Room.jpg","<p>Great for groups of friends, these rooms can accommodate up to six people. They still have their original extra-thick walls – to keep you cool in summer and toasty-warm in winter.</p>"),array("Standard room","https://karmagroup.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/09/Karma-Rottnest-Standard_Room.jpg","<p>Perfect for solo travellers or couples, these rooms are located in the historic Palm Court area, adjacent to the main lodge building. Each features either a double or twin beds.</p>")));

