//10.Karma St. Martin's - Isles of Scilly
$id="914";
$bannerImages=array("https://karmagroup.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Karma-St.Martins-Room.jpg","https://karmagroup.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Karma-St.-Martins.jpg","https://karmagroup.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Karma-St.Martins-Garden.jpg");
$title = "Karma St. Martin’s, Isles of Scilly";
$subTitle = "Luxury Beachside Resort in Isles of Scilly";
$description = "<h3>A subtropical island of white sand beaches and crystal clear seas, St. Martin’s redefines the luxury European escape.</h3>
<p>A holistic hideaway in an area of outstanding natural beauty, Karma St. Martin’s is a stone’s throw from the beach and a world apart from everyday life. From a distance, our newest resort appears as a hamlet of traditional stone cottages. Step inside and it’s revealed as a luxurious contemporary hotel, complete with ocean views, classic English interior design (with an eclectic twist) and a soulful Karma Spa. Relax…</p>";

$amenities=array("<p>Built in local stone to resemble a hamlet on the beach, Karma St. Martin’s is dotted across 2.8 hectares of hillside with panoramic views towards Tean Sound and Tresco. There are 27 four-star hotel rooms and three suites, perfect for families, couples and honeymooners. You can bring your dog, too; all our accommodation is pet friendly.</p>",array(array("Karma St. Martin’s bar","<p>Choose from our bespoke cocktail menu or enjoy the ultimate tasting experience in our wine lounge, where the Wine Emotion System dispenses perfectly kept wines by the glass, allowing you to explore the world’s finest vintages one sip at a time.</p>","https://karmagroup.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/ksm-bar-rev.jpg","",""),array("Karma collections","<p>Be DJ for the night and get the party started with our unique Karma vinyl collection, or borrow some bedtime reading from our library. We won’t mind if you turn down the corners on our books…</p>","https://karmagroup.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Karma-St-Martin-Karma-Collections.jpg","",""),array("Scuba or Snorkel with seals","<p>Get mask to whisker with Atlantic grey seals in the clear Scillonian waters. Guests of Karma St. Martin’s receive an exclusive 10 per cent discount when booking snorkelling with seals.</p>
<p>For those who like to dive, there is also the opportunity to scuba with seals off the shores of St. Martin&#8217;s&#8230;</p>","https://karmagroup.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/vcnbgRHFrpcDReRg-36AHbLLSuSWPkhhaZHfP-h4nRI.jpg","",""),array("Watersports","<p>Diving, rowing, windsurfing, sea swimming, sailing and more… The Isles of Scilly archipelago has countless opportunities to get wet and wild; just tell our Guest Services team know what you’d like to try. Or keep close to your home-from-home and let us pack you a picnic to enjoy on one of St. Martin’s powdery soft beaches.</p>","https://karmagroup.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Karma-St-Martin-Watersports.jpg","",""),array("Art & culture","<p>The stunning light and location attracts artists and craftspeople to the Isles of Scilly. Look out for collectable handmade silver jewellery, ceramics, stained glass and fine art. On St. Martin’s, the island’s artists are showcased in North Farm Gallery.</p>","https://karmagroup.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Karma-St-Martin-Art-Culture.jpg","",""),array("Karma Spa","<p>Make your selection from our magical menu of soulful therapies and treatments. We seek to create experiences for you that enhance your inner health and external beauty. All our Karma treatments are curated from ingredients sourced from ethical and sustainable growers and are paraben-free&#8230;</p>","https://karmagroup.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/spa-specialists.jpg","",""),array("Dog Friendly Destination","<p>Taking the dog with you on holiday shouldn&#8217;t mean being cooped up in a caravan park or a bare-boned B&amp;B. Karma St Martin&#8217;s hotel in the Cornish Isles of Scilly extends a warm welcome to its canine clientele. Karma&#8217;s stunning natural setting, creature comforts, and tranquil surroundings will leave you and your furry friend feeling like &#8216;Top-Dog&#8217;.</p>","https://karmagroup.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/KSM_DOG_LandingPage_161121.jpg","","")));

$accomodation=array("Luxury rooms and suites","<p>Classic English style, with the unique Karma spirit, means every room is the essence of luxury. Karma St. Martin’s features 4 Deluxe Rooms, 21 Ocean Rooms, 2 Superior Ocean Rooms, 2 Family Suites and a Honeymoon Suite.</p>",array(array("Deluxe Room","https://karmagroup.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Karma-St-Martin-Standard-Room.jpg","<p>Nestled at the heart of Karma St. Martin’s, these charming rooms have exteriors traditionally built from local stone and stylish contemporary interiors.</p>"),array("Ocean Room","https://karmagroup.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Karma-St-Martin-Ocean-Room.jpg","<p>Enjoy incredible comfort and stunning sea views. Four of our Ocean Rooms interconnect, giving greater flexibility when travelling with family and friends.</p>"),array("Superior Ocean Room","https://karmagroup.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Karma-St-Martin-Superior-Ocean-Room.jpg","<p>Luxurious rooms, with a sofa, en-suite bathroom and sea views.</p>"),array("Family Suite","https://karmagroup.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/KSM0018-1024x683.jpg","<p>The ideal choice when travelling with children, featuring a bedroom, plus living room with sofa bed.</p>"),array("Honeymoon Suite","https://karmagroup.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Karma-St-Martin-Honeymoon-Suite.jpg","<p>Luxurious bedroom with en-suite, large living room, panoramic views of Tean Sound and Lighthouse, plus a private balcony.</p>")));

$contactUs=array("<p>Isles of Scilly, Lower Town,<br />St Martin's, TR25 0QW,<br />England</p>","Resort Direct Dial: <br />+44 (0)3 333 232 353 (Toll Free)","","49.966304","-6.303521");
