//12.Karma Royal Bella Vista - Thailand
$id="1012";
$bannerImages=array("https://karmagroup.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/banner-2.jpg","https://karmagroup.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/bella-vista-1.jpg","https://karmagroup.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Karma-Royal-Chiang-Mai-Headline-c.jpg");
$title = "Karma Royal Bella Vista - Thailand";
$subTitle = "";
$description = "<p><hr3>Karma Royal Bella Vista is a peaceful oasis just outside of Chiang Mai, comprising of unique home-style cottages and comfortably appointed hotel rooms.</hr3></p><p>You'll also enjoy our facilities - including the spa, gym and restaurant – as you look out over Karma Royal Bella Vista's cobbled streets, gently flowing streams and lush gardens. There's no better place from which to explore Thailand's spiritual heartland, including some 300 Buddhist temples in the surrounding region, plus the unique shopping, arts and culture to be found in Chiang Mai’s old city.</p>";

$amenities=array("<p>From a leisurely swim to a game of tennis, take life at your own pace at Karma Chiang Mai.</p>",array(array("Swimming Pools","<p>There are two pools to choose from, each one surrounded by tropical palm trees and with plenty of loungers and seats to relax on.</p>","https://karmagroup.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/1._Pool-683x1024.jpg","",""),array("Karma Spa","<p>Indulgent spa therapies, massage and beauty treatments available in the beautifully styled onsite spa.</p>","https://karmagroup.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Karma-Royal-Chiang-Mai-Karma-Spa.jpg","",""),array("Tennis Court","<p>A knockabout or championship match; the ball’s in your court.</p>","https://karmagroup.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Karma-Royal-Chiang-Mai-Tennis-Court.jpg","",""),array("Library","<p>A fantastic collection from the book swap counter, a selection of music and DVDs for you to take back to your room and enjoy.</p>","https://karmagroup.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/jimbaran-Library-2.jpg","",""),array("Elephant Trekking","<p>A truly magical experience. There is nothing quite as serene as exploring the lush jungle by elephant as it picks its way through the trees.</p>","https://karmagroup.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Elephant-Trekking.jpg","",""),array("Shuttle bus to Chiang Mai City","<p>Regular Shuttle buses are available to take you the 40 minute drive to historic Chiang Mai, where you can explore its ancient moated city and incredible temples.</p>","https://karmagroup.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Karma-Royal-Chiang-Mai-Shuttle-Bus-to-Chiang-Mai.jpg","",""),array("Excursions","<p>Our onsite team has information on a host of activities for you to enjoy in Chiang Mai, on request. Activities include Thai cookery classes and a visit to the mountain top Doi Suthep shrine, which is one hours drive away. The resort is within striking distance of the fabled Golden Triangle which is a days excursion leaving early and returning late.</p>","https://karmagroup.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Excursions.jpg","",""),array("Bird watching and tropical Flora and Fauna","<p>Explore the tropical flora, fauna and bird life within the hotel grounds. The botanical gardens are also a marvel to behold and are only 20 minutes drive away.</p>","https://karmagroup.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Bird-Watching-Tropical-Flora-Founa.jpg","","")));

$accomodation=array("Accommodation","<p>Karma Royal Bella Vista offers diverse accommodation styles for solos, couples and families of all ages. Each designed with relaxation in mind, choose from a series of unique home-style cottages and comfortably appointed hotel rooms.</p>",array(array("Cottages","https://karmagroup.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/cottage-1024x768.jpg","<p>Each cottage has two bedrooms, a living room, kitchen and private patio, and is attractively furnished in a mixture of classic and modern Thai style.</p>
<p>Apartment amenities include:</p><ul class='light_blue_text'><li>Mini kitchen, Barbecue in each villa</li><li>Private garden patio</li><li>Open fireplace</li><li>Telephone (mobile)</li><li>Air conditioning (in 2 bedrooms and living room)</li><li>Flat-screen TV</li><li>Cable TV</li>
<li>DVD/iPod player</li><li>Free Wifi</li></ul>"),array("Superior rooms","https://karmagroup.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/two-bed-150x150.jpg","<p>Room size 37 sqm, 8 feet' king size bed, extra bed available, TV, DVD, Microwave, Kettle, Mini Fridge,Safty box, chair & table in Balcony, Iron & Iron Broad.</p>"),array("Special rooms","https://karmagroup.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/special-room-150x150.jpg","<p>Room size 50 sqm, 8 feet' king size bed, extra bed available, TV, DVD, Microwave, Kettle, Mini Fridge, Safty box, chair & table in Balcony, Iron & Iron Broad.</p>")));

